MAKGEOLLI 1

Measure out 200g Nuruk
Add 600ml water to Nuruk
Let sit for 4-7hrs


MISE

Pour 200ml white wine
pour 200ml cream
Shred 500g Potatoes
Slice 250g Mushrooms
Toss Mushrooms in 1Tbsp Flour
Chop 1 onion
Chop Parsley
Grate Lemon Peel
Slice 600g Pork



COOK

ROSTI

Fry Pan Med High Heat
Clarified Butter
Add Potatoes
Fry till golden
Remove to plate

GESCHNETZELTES

Fry Pan High Heat
Clarified Butter
Sear meat on both sides
Remove

Medium Heat
Sweat onions
Sautee Mushrooms
Deglaze with wine
Reduce by half
Add cream
Reduce by 1/4
Add Lemon Zest
Add Meat
Mix to coat
Sprinkle with Parsley

PLATE

PHOTO

WRAPUP


MAKGEOLLI 2

Drain nuruk
Save water

Weigh 1kg Chapssal
Wash till clear
Drain for 1hr

Line steamer with cheesecloth
Add rice
Steam for 40min (start timer when steam comes up)
Turn off heat
Let sit for 10min
Cool Rice to 77F

Sterilize jar

Add Nuruk water to rice
Mix thoroughly
Add to jar

Ferment for 7-10 days

